   "source": [
    "# Rave Health Analysis — Simplified Methodology + Predictive Models\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook cleans the event-level rave dataset, joins it to sleep/health data, creates recovery windows around each event, engineers interpretable metrics, builds an intensity score, and fits lightweight predictive models.\n",
    "\n",
    "Because this is a small personal dataset, the modeling section is exploratory. The goal is not to claim causal effects. The goal is to learn patterns, generate hypotheses, and make future event planning more data-informed."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "9875b92a",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
