   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "0952235a",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 5. Create event-centered recovery windows\n",
    "\n",
    "For every rave date, this creates sleep/health values for:\n",
    "- `-1`: the day before the event\n",
    "- `+0`: the event day\n",
    "- `+1`: the day after\n",
    "- `+2`: two days after\n",
    "- `+3`: three days after\n",
    "\n",
    "These offset columns let us compare baseline vs. post-event recovery."
   ]
  },
